data.description: Adorable well maintained ranch style home nestled in a quiet established community. Features 3 bedroom, 2 full baths, .97 acre lot, huge fenced back yard. Open concept kitchen, cozy family room w/ gas fireplace. Plenty of backyard extending beyond fence!! New Roof, New Water Heater, 15 mins from Wake County, 15 mins from Lake Royale! Plenty of land to create the epitome of country living!
